commitResults.messageBody:
Update AboutUs

Current AboutUs is a template and is bare.

Let's add in our profile pictures, GitHub links and our roles to the document.

Having a detailed AboutUs will allow others to become familiar with us and our work.

Update Developer Guide Glossary

Current glossary is a template and is not suited to our product.

Let's add in key terminologies and their definitions.

Having a detailed glossary will allow us to stay on the same page and minimise confusion.

Add in tips command to display a random tip to users.

Tips are stored internally and are retrieved randomly.
